<refentry id="bif.StrategyNumber" xreflabel="StrategyNumber">

<refmeta>
<indexterm>
<primary>StrategyNumber</primary>
</indexterm>

<refentrytitle>StrategyNumber</refentrytitle>
<refmiscinfo>Built-in function</refmiscinfo>
</refmeta>

<refnamediv>
<refname>StrategyNumber</refname>
<refpurpose>
Returns the index of a strategy in a support
</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
<synopsis>
StrategyNumber[strategy->STRATEGY, sup->NFSUPPORT] =: INTEGER
</synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1><title>Description</title>
<para>
<function>StrategyNumber</function>
returns the number assigned to <parameter>strategy</parameter> in the support
<parameter>sup</parameter>.  Strategies  for each player are numbered from 1 to
the number of strategies for the player.  If a strategy is not in
the corresponding support, it is assigned a number of 0.
</para>
</refsect1>

